\c 3
\s Vana vaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaDhavhidhi, vakamuberekerwa paHebhuroni: Wedangwe Amunoni, mwana waAhinoami muJezireeri; wechipiri Dhanyeri waAbhigairi muKarimeri;
\v 2 wechitatu Abhusaromu mwanakomana waMaaka, mukunda waTarimai mambo weGeshuri; wechina Adhonia mwanakomana waHagiti;
\v 3 weshanu Shefatia waAbhitari, wetanhatu Itireami kuna Egira mukadzi wake.
\p
\v 4 Wakaberekerwa vatanhatu paHebhuroni, akabata ushepo makore manomwe nemwedzi mitanhatu; akabata ushe paJerusaremu makore makumi matatu namatatu.
\v 5 Ava ndivo vaakaberekerwa paJerusaremu: Shimea, naShobhabhi, naNatani, naSoromoni, ivo vana, vaBhatishua mukunda waAmieri;
\v 6 naIbhari, naErishama, naErifereti;
\v 7 naNoga, naNefegi, naJafia;
\v 8 naErishama, naEriadha, naErifereti, ivo vapfumbamwe.
\p
\v 9 Ndivo vose vaiva vana vaDhavhidhi, vanakomana vavarongo vasingaverengwi; uye Tamari wakanga ari hanzvadzi yavo.
\p
\v 10 Mwanakomana waSoromoni akanga ari Rehobhoami, mwanakomana wake Abhia, mwanakomana wake Asa, mwanakomana wake Jehoshafati;
\v 11 mwanakomana wake Joramu, mwanakomana wake Ahazia, mwanakomana wake Joashi;
\v 12 mwanakomana wake Amazia, mwanakomana wake Azaria, mwanakomana wake Jotamu;
\v 13 mwanakomana wake Ahazi, mwanakomana wake Hezekia, mwanakomana wake Manase;
\v 14 mwanakomana wake Amoni, mwanakomana wake Josia.
\v 15 Vanakomana vaJosia: Wedangwe Johanani, wechipiri Jehoyakimu, wechitatu Zedhekia, wechina Sharumi.
\p
\v 16 Vanakomana vaJehoyakimu: Mwanakomana wake Jekonia, mwanakomana wake Zedhekia.
\p
\v 17 Vanakomana vaJekonia, vakatapwa. Shearitieri mwanakomana wake,
\v 18 naMarikirami, naPedhaya, naShenazari, Jekamia, Hoshama, naNedhabhia.
\v 19 Vanakomana vaPedhaya: Zerubhabheri, naShimei; vanakomana vaZerubhabheri: Meshurami, naHanania; uye Sheromiti akanga ari hanzvadzi yavo;
\v 20 naHashubha, naOheri, naBherekia, naHasadhia, naJushabhiheshedhi, ivo vashanu.
\p
\v 21 Vanakomana vaHanania: Peratia, naJeshaya; vanakomana vaRefaya, vanakomana vaArinani, vanakomana vaObhadhiya, vanakomana vaShekania.
\v 22 Vanakomana vaShekania: Shemaya; navanakomana vaShemaya; Hatushi, naIgari, naBharia, naNearia, naShafati, ivo vatanhatu.
\p
\v 23 Vanakomana vaNearia: Erioenai, naHizikia, naAzirikami, ivo vatatu.
\p
\v 24 Vanakomana vaErioenai: Hodhavhia, naEriashibhi, naPeraya, naAkubhi, naJohanani, naDheraya, naAnani, ivo vanomwe.
